# C# conventions

- Namespace: `JobsGeParser` root; subfolders use matching namespaces (`Configuration`, `Models`, `Data`, `Scraping`, `Endpoints`, `Endpoints.Dtos`, `Workers`)
- Nullable enabled — avoid null-forgiving unless justified
- New config: `JobsGeParserOptions` + appsettings.json + validation in `Configuration/DependencyInjection`
- New services: singleton unless stateless/scoped need arises (DbContext, Repo, JobsGeClient are scoped)
- Use IHttpClientFactory named client "JobsGeClient" — no new static HttpClient fields
- Prefer extension methods on IServiceCollection / IEndpointRouteBuilder (match `DependencyInjection.cs` pattern)
